(5753, 247, 'Important information about your order with PlusPro', '<style>\nbody,td { font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; }\r\na { color: #330066; }\r\n.wrapper {\r\nwidth:650px; \r\n}\n</style>\n<div style="width:650px;margin:0 auto;">\r\n<p><a href="http://www.pluspro.com" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.plusprowebsites.com/img/pluspro_logo.jpg" alt="PlusPro (Monara IT UK Ltd)" border="0" /></a></p>\n<p>Dear Alex Barry (KP Classic &amp; Modern LTD),</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for choosing PlusPro as your website partner. Please read the step by step information below which is a guide to our procedures along with what to expect next:</p>\r\n<div style="background: #f6f6f6; border: 1px solid #000; padding: 10px; margin: 35px 0px;">\r\n<p style="font-size: 10px;"><strong>Step One:</strong> Designing your website.<br /><br /> Immediately upon receiving your order our design team will start the task of creating the design for your website. Because we create custom designs for our clients this process usually takes up to 14 days to complete. <br /> <strong>Please note: </strong>During this phase we will be contacting you so that you can approve the design. Please respond as promptly as possible as we do not proceed to the next step until we have your approval.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 10px; margin-top: 30px;"><strong>Step Two:</strong> Creating the website.<br /><br /> As soon as you have approved the design we will pass your project over to our programming team. Your design will now be turned into a working website and integrated into our Content Management System (CMS) and any required custom programming will be undertaken. Please allow up to 28 days for this process to be completed.</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 10px; margin-top: 30px;"><strong>Step Three:</strong> Hand-over stage.<br /><br /> Your website is now ready to go! We will contact you at this stage and provide instruction on how to operate your CMS and site admin fu